{"tid":344744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奧運女神] 歐凱淳fb唔少心自貼露西相","createTime":"2017-08-02T13:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T01:21:49.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81e46c470a0d7051095d5234d43ca460c3ea0927","tid":344744,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/210408_4d7bfb30b9844eb453690078f14ec42a.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F210408_4d7bfb30b9844eb453690078f14ec42a.jpg&d=u%2F1HYRBVLHCuqs5ou2zj7J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f9eaef73\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/210408_4d7bfb30b9844eb453690078f14ec42a.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n【小鎧淳飛奔泳池】<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知我第一個奬牌係點嚟架呢？佢係一個區賽50米蛙式嘅銅牌，嗰次令我嘅游水生涯從此變得不一樣，仲夠晒「驚心動魄」。<br />\n媽咪憶述當日係港島區游泳區賽嘅日子，但係媽咪爹哋竟然差啲忘記咗！我地上氣唔接下氣咁趕到比賽現場，啱啱好趕得切召集同比賽，點估到嗰一個就係我人生第一個奬牌。如果泳池近屋企多啲，我就唔駛咁趕，可能我嘅奬牌顏色會唔一樣？<br />\n<br />\n趕，又點止限於比賽&hellip;以前日日屋企去泳池，泳池去學校，學校去泳池，泳池返屋企&hellip;當年未做泳手，我已經了解「時間， 永遠係最大嘅敵人。」日日都咁趕咁攰，要堅持落去的確唔易，我成日都幻想，游泳池就喺我屋企隔離&hellip;<br />\n一出家門就有個50米游泳池，想幾時游就幾時游，仲有 24 小時健身室，如果真係有得住喺呢度，會唔會太幸褔？<br />\n<br />\n歐鎧淳 (Stephanie Au)<br />\n#WhereDreamsComeHome #KaiTak #夢想在家"},{"pid":"5e75742479c251444b2822001aed4b009f90534b","tid":344744,"uid":84951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"927668b1b5e65279735cc02c0ab8c843c0005d42","tid":344744,"uid":9284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"Jing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110d90dbf80eb8151d4f83a723d2e453b1808f90","tid":344744,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https